# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP response headers
# Headwaters Practitioner Intake Tool (artifacts/headwaters)
# Deployed root: thestompingpaths.com/headwaters/
# As a standalone CF Pages project, paths below are relative to its own root (/).
#
# STUB — committed for migration readiness. Review before deploying.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
